"{\"uid\": \"slate.com-culture-2024-07-olympics-paris-seine-sewage-triathlon-e-coli-safe-swimming.html\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"This is part of Slate's 2024 Olympics coverage.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 47, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 16, \"end\": 21, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slate\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.869083760835954e-44, \"text\": \"Slate\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slate\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slate\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 8, \"to\": 12}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read morehere.\", \"from\": 48, \"to\": 62, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you are enjoying our coverage from Paris, joinSlate Plusto support our work.\", \"from\": 63, \"to\": 142, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 101, \"end\": 106, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3434318109288112e-37, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our coverage\", \"from\": 83, \"to\": 95}, {\"ngram\": \"our work\", \"from\": 133, \"to\": 141}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They swam in the damn Seine.\", \"from\": 144, \"to\": 172, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 166, \"end\": 171, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.602255693597639e-42, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At 8 a.m. Wednesday, 55 women dove in under a heavy gray sky.\", \"from\": 173, \"to\": 234, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"8 a.m.\", \"from\": 176, \"to\": 182}, {\"ngram\": \"55 women\", \"from\": 194, \"to\": 202}, {\"ngram\": \"a heavy gray sky\", \"from\": 217, \"to\": 233}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The city was quiet except for the buzzing of the helicopters overhead, and spectators with binoculars roamed the bridges and thequaisalongside curious commuters.\", \"from\": 235, \"to\": 396, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The city\", \"from\": 235, \"to\": 243}, {\"ngram\": \"the buzzing\", \"from\": 265, \"to\": 276}, {\"ngram\": \"the helicopters\", \"from\": 280, \"to\": 295}, {\"ngram\": \"spectators\", \"from\": 310, \"to\": 320}, {\"ngram\": \"binoculars\", \"from\": 326, \"to\": 336}, {\"ngram\": \"the bridges\", \"from\": 344, \"to\": 355}, {\"ngram\": \"thequaisalongside curious commuters\", \"from\": 360, \"to\": 395}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As the swimmers came downstream, they moved in a tight splashing pack like fish jumping or rapids for the race helpers in their kayaks.\", \"from\": 397, \"to\": 532, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the swimmers\", \"from\": 400, \"to\": 412}, {\"ngram\": \"a tight splashing pack\", \"from\": 444, \"to\": 466}, {\"ngram\": \"fish jumping\", \"from\": 472, \"to\": 484}, {\"ngram\": \"rapids\", \"from\": 488, \"to\": 494}, {\"ngram\": \"the race helpers\", \"from\": 499, \"to\": 515}, {\"ngram\": \"their kayaks\", \"from\": 519, \"to\": 531}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But as they turned to cross the river, then upstream, the separation began: Now they were swimming against a powerful current running at just under a meter a second.\", \"from\": 533, \"to\": 698, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 570}, {\"ngram\": \"the separation\", \"from\": 587, \"to\": 601}, {\"ngram\": \"a powerful current\", \"from\": 640, \"to\": 658}, {\"ngram\": \"a meter\", \"from\": 681, \"to\": 688}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It felt like a treadmill.\", \"from\": 699, \"to\": 724, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a treadmill\", \"from\": 712, \"to\": 723}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The water tests came in at 3:20 a.m. Wednesday.\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 773, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The water tests\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 741}, {\"ngram\": \"3:20 a.m.\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 762}]}, {\"sentence\": \"World Triathlon, the city and regional government, and the French weather serviceconvened, for the fourth day in a row, at 3:30 a.m. And the flagship promise of the 2024 Paris Games-swimming competitions in a restored Seine, in the shadow of the Eiffel Tower-came true at the unholy hour of4:14 a.m., less than four hours before the women's triathlon race began.\", \"from\": 774, \"to\": 1137, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 774, \"end\": 789, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Triathlon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.539247198696265e-18, \"text\": \"World Triathlon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Triathlon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Triathlon\"}, {\"begin\": 833, \"end\": 839, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9994117341142146, \"rank\": 0.0005528144626764889, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 993, \"end\": 998, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.602255693597639e-42, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 791, \"to\": 799}, {\"ngram\": \"regional government\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 823}, {\"ngram\": \"the fourth day\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 883}, {\"ngram\": \"a row\", \"from\": 887, \"to\": 892}, {\"ngram\": \"3:30 a.m.\", \"from\": 897, \"to\": 906}, {\"ngram\": \"the flagship promise\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 931}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Paris Games-swimming competitions\", \"from\": 935, \"to\": 977}, {\"ngram\": \"the shadow\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1012}, {\"ngram\": \"the unholy hour of4:14\", \"from\": 1046, \"to\": 1068}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's triathlon race\", \"from\": 1103, \"to\": 1129}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's an hour not known for sound decisionmaking, and critics have alleged a sudden lack of transparency from officials about water quality.\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1278, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an hour\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1151}, {\"ngram\": \"sound\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1171}, {\"ngram\": \"critics\", \"from\": 1192, \"to\": 1199}, {\"ngram\": \"a sudden lack\", \"from\": 1213, \"to\": 1226}, {\"ngram\": \"transparency\", \"from\": 1230, \"to\": 1242}, {\"ngram\": \"officials\", \"from\": 1248, \"to\": 1257}, {\"ngram\": \"water quality\", \"from\": 1264, \"to\": 1277}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After two months of weekly reports from the city of Paris, the Paris 2024 Olympics organizers havestopped publishing data.\", \"from\": 1279, \"to\": 1401, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1331, \"end\": 1336, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3434318109288112e-37, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two months\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1295}, {\"ngram\": \"weekly reports\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1313}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 1319, \"to\": 1327}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris 2024 Olympics organizers\", \"from\": 1338, \"to\": 1372}, {\"ngram\": \"publishing data\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1400}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But right at 8 a.m., as the women took their places on the platform beneath the gilded statues of the Pont Alexandre III, the debate stopped and the sport began.\", \"from\": 1403, \"to\": 1564, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1505, \"end\": 1523, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pont_Alexandre_III\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pont Alexandre III\", \"